   "source": [
    "# 🏦 AML/KYC Transaction Classification Engine\n",
    "### AI-Powered Risk & Compliance Assistant for Retail Banking\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook tests the deterministic AML/KYC prompt against the synthetic dataset.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Cells in this notebook:**\n",
    "1. Install dependencies\n",
    "2. Setup API key\n",
    "3. Define the master prompt\n",
    "4. Define the full dataset (20 transactions)\n",
    "5. Single transaction tester\n",
    "6. Batch runner (all 20 transactions)\n",
    "7. Results comparison against expected outputs\n",
    "8. Customer-level summary"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## Cell 1 — Install Dependencies"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
